beer.beer_name: Double Dry Hopped All Citra Everything
beer.beer_description: Our standard All Citra Everything double dry hopped with an extra dose of Citra lupulin powder.

Light and fluffly like fresh fallen snow we stocked with one full of malted oats, flaked wheat and milk sugar. We slung some Denali and Cyro Citra in the whirlpool then used a snow fort's worth of Denali, Mosaic and Cryo Citra through multiple dry hops with a snowflake's kiss of Motueka at the end and conditioned on silky Madagascar Vanilla. Tropical and citrus snow clouds.
Hey! You got your ACE in my Space Diamonds. No! You got your Space in my ACE. Delicious! Two great tastes that taste great together. Real Citra and good old fashioned galaxy.

A Double Dry-Hopped version of our Water Balloon Fighters Double IPA with Mosaic, Citra, & Simcoe hops. 
This is batch 6.
